{
  "stem": "3605.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a very strong impression on me made a incident-- this was-- I was at that time not quite 12 years old, and we had a parade in our school.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my brother was carrying the Polish flag on the streets of our town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a hoodlum threw-- a Polish hoodlum-- threw a knife right through his earlobe.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He could have killed him-- that a Jew should not carry a Polish flag.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This kind of changed my outlook, and I became very strongly attached to a Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Zionist organization's name was Akiba.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a lot of my friends belonged there too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it took up-- took up a lot of my social life and energy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And being that my mother was busy in the business, and my father was travelling a whole week, that filled in quite a lot of my time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] When-- in 1939, during the summer vacation, there was already starting a-- a talk-- a talk about a possibility of war was starting.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Of course, before that, there were news in the papers about the prosecution of the Jews in Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But, of course, we were people of hope, and we always thought that this is over there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And nothing is going to come to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did believe, because it was in the [NON-ENGLISH] that was such a-- weekly that showed it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- it was also the-- the [NON-ENGLISH] was writing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some people got the news-- the German newspaper, and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, we believed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was not something that we thought it's the end of the world.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very disturbing and very bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
